P_HTM[972]="*Ime kho, bhikkhave, dve paṇḍitā”ti.**These are the two who are astute.”*";
P_HTM[973]="*108**108*";
P_HTM[974]="*“Dvinnaṃ, bhikkhave, āsavā vaḍḍhanti.**“For these two, defilements grow.*";
P_HTM[975]="*Katamesaṃ dvinnaṃ?**What two?*";
P_HTM[976]="*Yo ca na kukkuccāyitabbaṃ kukkuccāyati, yo ca kukkuccāyitabbaṃ na kukkuccāyati.**One who is remorseful over something they shouldn’t be, and one who isn’t remorseful over something they should be.*";
P_HTM[977]="*Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, dvinnaṃ āsavā vaḍḍhantī”ti.**These are the two whose defilements grow.”*";
P_HTM[978]="*109**109*";
P_HTM[979]="*“Dvinnaṃ, bhikkhave, āsavā na vaḍḍhanti.**“For these two, defilements don’t grow.*";
P_HTM[980]="*Katamesaṃ dvinnaṃ?**What two?*";
P_HTM[981]="*Yo ca na kukkuccāyitabbaṃ na kukkuccāyati, yo ca kukkuccāyitabbaṃ kukkuccāyati.**One who isn’t remorseful over something they shouldn’t be, and one who is remorseful over something they should be.*";
P_HTM[982]="*Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, dvinnaṃ āsavā na vaḍḍhantī”ti.**These are the two whose defilements don’t grow.”*";
